MZANSI people are divided over videos of a helper known as Thembi and his mlungu boss Malcolm. Thembi’s boss posted several videos featuring himself and Thembi engaged in several activities. It appears the videos were meant for fun but other people on social media believe they are in a bad taste. In one of the videos, Thembi is seen driving her boss's car while in another, Thembi gets to choose an expensive champagne for the weekend. There’s other video clips where she pours him with water when he is sleeping and where they dance together. This videos drew mixed reactions on twitter and sparked a debate between those who love the videos and those who despises them. Those who hated the videos called them racist and patronizing while others said they were just fun and there was nothing wrong with them.        